sentences.english: Jian Shilong, director of China Maritime Tracking and Control Department, said the ships would track and support Shenzhou VII, and monitor the spacewalk.
sentences.chinese: 定位船将负责跟踪支援神舟七号，并指挥太空行走。

sentences.english: Shenzhou (Divine Vessel) consists of the Orbital Module.
sentences.chinese: 神舟号包括轨道舱，返回舱和推进舱。

sentences.english: The name of the spaceship is Shenzhou V.
sentences.chinese: 宇宙飞船的名字是“神舟五号”。

sentences.english: But that could change on one of the next Shenzhou docking missions.
sentences.chinese: 但是，下一次神舟对接任务中，这个情况会发生变化。

sentences.english: It is exciting that we have succeeded in sending up Shenzhou V.
sentences.chinese: 我们成功地发射了神舟五号这件事情真令人兴奋。

sentences.english: China has announced that the Shenzhou-7 spacecraft will on Thursday night.
sentences.chinese: 中国已经宣布神舟七号飞船将于周四晚上发射。

sentences.english: Live recordings of China's Shenzhou 7 Space Mission.
sentences.chinese: 中国神舟7号宇宙飞船的实况录像。

sentences.english: Shenzhou (Divine Vessel) consists of the Orbital Module, Re-entry Module and Propelling Module.
sentences.chinese: 神舟号包括轨道舱，返回舱和舱。

sentences.english: I announce the launch of Shenzhou-11 manned spacecraft is a complete success.
sentences.chinese: 我宣布，神舟十一号载人飞船发射取得圆满成功。

sentences.english: shenzhou (divine vessel) consists of the orbital module, re-entry module and propelling module.
sentences.chinese: 神舟号包括轨道舱，返回舱和推进舱。

sentences.english: The spacecraft will return to Earth after two docking operations.
sentences.chinese: 神舟八号将在完成两次对接任务后返回地球。

sentences.english: China has announced that the Shenzhou-7 spacecraft will lift off on Thursday night.
sentences.chinese: 中国已经宣布神舟七号飞船将于周四晚上发射。
